description: Samuel O'Toole is throwing a party! And not just any party, but a themed out blacklight party. He's got the room all set up and the party is in a few days, but he just can't wait to try it out. So he lures Dominic Pacifico down into his blacklight dungeon, where Dominic discovers that Samuel has a few tricks up his sleeve, as well as one gigantic trick down his pants.Enjoy!
title: Day Glo Fuck Party
